name: Jigsaw Estrela
description:
Solve and discover Serra da Estrela. The biggest mountain in Portugal. 

I walked 14 km to reach this location, one of the few in Portugal where I can capture the entire length of the mountain. The picture and video was captured with my Smartphone. 

Artist: notaDevOrArtist
Created/Release: January 25 2022
Medium: p5.js, html canvas, css (video capture)

#7 from the Jigsaw Puzzle series

Note: Works on any device, however it can take a few seconds to load the video.
